left2\">香型：董香型 <br />\r\n            酒精度：41%vol<br />\r\n            净含量：500ml <br />\r\n            产地：贵州遵义<br />\r\n            原料：水、高粱、小麦、大米<br />\r\n            储存条件：通风、干燥、清洁、常温</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://bcs.baidu.com/weigou-prodb-image/product_desc_181594507_221389_2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"formwork_bt\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_bt_rb\"><span>产品特色</span><span class=\"s2\">Selling Point</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://bcs.baidu.com/weigou-prodb-image/product_desc_181594507_221389_3.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://bcs.baidu.com/weigou-prodb-image/product_desc_181594507_221389_4.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://bcs.baidu.com/weigou-prodb-image/product_desc_181594507_221389_5.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://bcs.baidu.com/weigou-prodb-image/product_desc_181594507_221389_6.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork_bt\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_bt_rb\"><span>品牌荣誉</span><span class=\"s2\">Brand Awards</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://bcs.baidu.com/weigou-prodb-image/product_desc_181594507_221389_7.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://bcs.baidu.com/weigou-prodb-image/product_desc_181594507_221389_8.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_tpl_left1\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_tp1_img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://bcs.baidu.com/weigou-prodb-image/product_desc_181594507_221389_9.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201404/thumb_img/479_thumb_G_1398127380506.jpg',